What are some of the ways you can balance your efforts to achieve virtue through acceptance of yourself?\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Accept I haven\'92t always treated others with fairness & respect despite \'91doing the right thing\'92 being what I stand for.\
Accept that despite every effort some people/outcomes/perceptions cannot be reached.\
Accept that I haven\'92t as yet taken action that I could have to improve those things I want.\
Accept that I haven\'92t really sacrificed anything significant.\
Accept that life hasn\'92t provided much of a test to my resilience.\
Accept that I haven\'92t walked the walk of the can-do attitude I promote.\
Accept that I carry a lot of bias that need checking.\
Accept that I\'92m not always right.\
Accept that I have to seek opportunities to present/demonstrate self control otherwise it passes because I do not see the opportunity.\
